0vw, 2000px" /></p><p>运河船上的唱片店“Rubber Ducky Records” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rubber-ducky-records-launches-fundraiser-after-canal-boat-sinks-3440831">去年沉没</a>后重新开业。</p><p>创始人迈尔斯·格林伍德 (Myles Greenwood) 宣布，该商店已在 Facebook 上重新开业，游客现在可以开始预约，再次仔细阅读船上的记录。</p><p> “我非常感谢自沉没以来所有的支持和慷慨，”格林伍德本月分享的一篇帖子中写道。 “无论是一条信息、GoFundMe 捐款还是一个拥抱，都非常感谢。人性真是不可思议。”</p><p> 4月份，即该船首次开业六个月后沉没，格林伍德通过 GoFundMe 筹集了 10,000 英镑用于修复该船。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C1MYCLLsPnW/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.